{"tid":422660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「叫你媽訂棺材」 台男生果刀割頸殺死女友老竇","createTime":"2017-10-03T09:13:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-06T12:51:23.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4e80aba6cbff67097041a75b97f45c928e6d7132","tid":422660,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T09:13:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171003/large/1507013726_3f95.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171003%2Flarge%2F1507013726_3f95.jpg&h=d18fa7d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171003/large/1507013728_a1c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171003%2Flarge%2F1507013728_a1c0.jpg&h=ffef9738&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">謝男行兇前與王女在facebook互罵，寫下「叫你媽可以先去訂棺材了，等等太臨時難買」。</span><br />\n<br />\n台灣桃園市平鎮區昨晚發生命案。男子謝榮賓（33歲）因王姓女友提出分手，兩人又有金錢瓜葛。王女事後避不見面，謝男因找不到王女，便把怒氣牽扯上王女的家人。<br />\n<br />\n謝男在過去2周多次前往王家的車房爭吵，昨晚8時許竟手持水果刀刺死王父。謝男行兇前與王女在facebook互罵，寫下：「叫你媽可以先去訂棺材了，等等太臨時難買！」沒想到一語成讖。<br />\n<br />\n事發時謝男拿一罐石油氣到王家車房，當時王父與2名兒子在泡茶，謝拿着打火機威脅點火要同歸於盡，王父與2名兒子衝出阻擋，雙方就在門口發生衝突。謝見寡不敵眾，突然從背包中抽出一把水果刀朝王父猛刺，沒想到一刀從頸部割斷氣管，王父送院後傷重不治。<br />\n<br />\n謝男行兇後左手骨折，負傷跑到衞福部桃園醫院求醫，昨晚被捕，今日訊後也以殺人罪移送地檢署偵辦。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">王家親友表示，王女已離家一年多，鮮與家人聯絡，謝男突然找上門也着實讓家裏感到非常困擾，沒想到會發生悲劇。親友稱，昨晚家裏電話告知王女她父親過世的消息時，王女居然直接掛斷電話，讓親友們聽了不斷搖頭。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171003/large/1507013731_3088.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171003%2Flarge%2F1507013731_3088.jpg&h=0987b763&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">謝家中秋節前辦喪事。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20171003/57285711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20171003%2F57285711&d=UZAdTXUFKOLvNuBFb7Lfs7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=0aa780a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20171003%2F57285711&h=07a4c075\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20171003/57285711</a><br />\n<br />\n死女包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a754242555c8d88b827a4748311fcda2c8d719a0","tid":422660,"uid":126293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T09:17:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66d514820333a7265973381c503106b1573b2e16","tid":422660,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T09:21:08.000Z","msg":"最緊要最尾買得到"},{"pid":"4040f561e0e0d2459bb23f4941b6426ffb6d287c","tid":422660,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T09:23:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 台狗"},{"pid":"bcf4f9155fc834a1bb6ecbe37b7781861b8991d3","tid":422660,"uid":110988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T09:30:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比個不肖女累死"},{"pid":"cce0518635c33c8adba9a18ab1dcd4f0cd0d0a43","tid":422660,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T09:32:03.000Z","msg":"條友真心廢 明明走左佬 小小骨折去醫院比人捉"},{"pid":"6e8d974e98a1c665cd1d724219a09a8047be6bd4","tid":422660,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T09:33:36.000Z","msg":"條仔都幾撚失敗<br />\n比條女呃錢呃感情 話要殺人老母<br />\n點知老母殺唔成變左殺老竇<br />\n最後原來條女完全都唔撚CARE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a966730efe7ed53103fdf8277de3663f1ca74b","tid":422660